{"tid":2212111,"cid":37,"subCid":13,"title":"租樓遇上個單位鑲咗鋁板","createTime":"2020-09-21T14:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T08:43:27.000Z","uid":25379,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a9621a85891e7681c4014ff2e9cd98b0b8977954","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"頭先落大雨去睇樓，業主有兩層畀我睇，兩層都有係一面牆鑲呂板。咁岩落大雨，見上層樓竟然有滲水，廳有少少，房都幾多。<br />\n我本身想租下層，下層就無滲水嘅，不過一樣係同一面牆有鋁板，大家覺得下層滲水機會大唔大？會唔會好多霉菌？<br />\n<br />\nPs, 有返咁上下樓齡，層樓剛翻新過。（不過照滲水）<br />\n<br />\n我應唔應該租好？"},{"pid":"45eadc6cfea7ba8a91ab25cc30bf7b34cbd021d7","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"2f7bd29051cea705dfcbc5d019d9969195f0c244","tid":2212111,"uid":239912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"唔應該租"},{"pid":"33aa78e4a595a7c51d181dcdf2e9f7cdae25a53d","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f7bd29051cea705dfcbc5d019d9969195f0c244","tid":2212111,"uid":239912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"唔應該租"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"有冇得講多少少<br />\n<br />\n我一條友，有諗過租一兩年，到佢真係出問題就搬<br />\n但又唔知就算無滲水一樣有霉菌，同會唔會好嚴重"},{"pid":"dfdb3fe529094bcd03f240eccb4bca6bf8efbb72","tid":2212111,"uid":51790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"又要擔心又要租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜一定要租果廣？"},{"pid":"a95e14327bfaf89d29878c208211f89b1c0752bf","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dfdb3fe529094bcd03f240eccb4bca6bf8efbb72","tid":2212111,"uid":51790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"又要擔心又要租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜一定要租果廣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"環境幾好，靚裝，價錢抵，我算係有啲心動"},{"pid":"6bfead6722692e748acc057ad7489a8ec46bcdf7","tid":2212111,"uid":239912,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"33aa78e4a595a7c51d181dcdf2e9f7cdae25a53d","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2f7bd29051cea705dfcbc5d019d9969195f0c244","tid":2212111,"uid":239912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"唔應該租"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"有冇得講多少少<br />\n<br />\n我一條友，有諗過租一兩年，到佢真係出問題就搬<br />\n但又唔知就算無滲水一樣有霉菌，同會唔會好嚴重"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:38:15.000Z","msg":"無事無幹做咩要鑲板？<br />\n到住落左真係滲水 就搵自己麻煩<br />\n到日後業主收番層樓 發現滲水 到時就話係你整爛人間屋 扣你按金屈你賠就煩<br />\n香港地好多仆街業主 一味靠屈"},{"pid":"ecd742df88ec0e272a9c7883372199ae8d48eeb6","tid":2212111,"uid":239912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a95e14327bfaf89d29878c208211f89b1c0752bf","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dfdb3fe529094bcd03f240eccb4bca6bf8efbb72","tid":2212111,"uid":51790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"又要擔心又要租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜一定要租果廣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"環境幾好，靚裝，價錢抵，我算係有啲心動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"邊有平靚正 <br />\n佢咁平租出去又有靚裝又有好環境<br />\n呢啲荀盤 經紀自己留左比熟客啦<br />\n仲點會流出街"},{"pid":"45ae6ea5884f2f9c0b007a2df933cfe1b5ed11fb","tid":2212111,"uid":188104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:41:21.000Z","msg":"大把盤啦<br />\n揀第二個"},{"pid":"1e004273df90db18f22ecb38f91337dc2141f895","tid":2212111,"uid":247471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:48:11.000Z","msg":"唔好租，租咗仲煩"},{"pid":"07331a5a9366297ac2dd6534664f588b41aafcee","tid":2212111,"uid":346260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，好大機會包括<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=b9931756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?唔該晒<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"931a2ef805ad33713654c257f4deb1911856ae37","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ecd742df88ec0e272a9c7883372199ae8d48eeb6","tid":2212111,"uid":239912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a95e14327bfaf89d29878c208211f89b1c0752bf","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"dfdb3fe529094bcd03f240eccb4bca6bf8efbb72","tid":2212111,"uid":51790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:29:16.000Z","msg":"又要擔心又要租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做乜一定要租果廣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"環境幾好，靚裝，價錢抵，我算係有啲心動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"邊有平靚正 <br />\n佢咁平租出去又有靚裝又有好環境<br />\n呢啲荀盤 經紀自己留左比熟客啦<br />\n仲點會流出街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"個經紀遲到，畀我遇上咗個業主，個婆婆問我咩事，我話嚟睇樓，然後佢就落樓攞鎖匙，無啦啦開咗第二間剛裝修好同準備放租的一間畀我睇，一問下先知原來成撞唐樓都係佢，我嚇咗跳。<br />\n<br />\n之後睇完樓，個經紀遲咗成三個字，然後同我睇返原本個間細劏房，我話唔啱，佢就帶個睇埋業主準備放，但仲有少少未好，問咗問價，個經紀講貴三千蚊，其實我再check同區價，真心平咗少少，我覺得如果係經個經紀去租，一定係比市價貴少少，因為靚裝。<br />\n<br />\n除非個婆婆好古惑，否則個婆婆真心大把錢，唔怕個幾千蚊租，只求好租客，佢有好幾個位都令我覺得好慈祥，我認我都相信佢嘅，都係個句，除非佢好古惑。"},{"pid":"4bbb38f1b6f809850aec7e1a7749ab3219a9eaa0","tid":2212111,"uid":239912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"931a2ef805ad33713654c257f4deb1911856ae37","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ecd742df88ec0e272a9c7883372199ae8d48eeb6","tid":2212111,"uid":239912,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a95e14327bfaf89d29878c208211f89b1c0752bf","tid":2212111,"uid":25379,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"環境幾好，靚裝，價錢抵，我算係有啲心動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:39:42.000Z","msg":"邊有平靚正 <br />\n佢咁平租出去又有靚裝又有好環境<br />\n呢啲荀盤 經紀自己留左比熟客啦<br />\n仲點會流出街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"個經紀遲到，畀我遇上咗個業主，個婆婆問我咩事，我話嚟睇樓，然後佢就落樓攞鎖匙，無啦啦開咗第二間剛裝修好同準備放租的一間畀我睇，一問下先知原來成撞唐樓都係佢，我嚇咗跳。<br />\n<br />\n之後睇完樓，個經紀遲咗成三個字，然後同我睇返原本個間細劏房，我話唔啱，佢就帶個睇埋業主準備放，但仲有少少未好，問咗問價，個經紀講貴三千蚊，其實我再check同區價，真心平咗少少，我覺得如果係經個經紀去租，一定係比市價貴少少，因為靚裝。<br />\n<br />\n除非個婆婆好古惑，否則個婆婆真心大把錢，唔怕個幾千蚊租，只求好租客，佢有好幾個位都令我覺得好慈祥，我認我都相信佢嘅，都係個句，除非佢好古惑。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:57:24.000Z","msg":"我寧願再搵 都唔會take 呢個risk"},{"pid":"fae29febf0d790